<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎯 Open-Gi-Oh! 平衡策略展示</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f97316, #eab308, #22d3ee);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .header .version {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #64748b;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .strategy-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .strategy-card {
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.9);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .strategy-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #22d3ee;
        }
        
        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
        }
        
        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #22d3ee;
        }
        
        .card-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        
        .strategy-content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .strategy-item {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .strategy-item:before {
            content: "•";
            color: #f97316;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .strategy-rule {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        
        .rule-fixed {
            border-left-color: #10b981;
        }
        
        .rule-negotiable {
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .rule-prohibited {
            border-left-color: #ef4444;
        }
        
        .rule-label {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .label-fixed {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            color: #10b981;
        }
        
        .label-negotiable {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
            color: #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .label-prohibited {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            color: #ef4444;
        }
        
        .cost-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .cost-table th {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
            color: #22d3ee;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .cost-table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cost-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .cost-table tr:hover {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
        }
        
        .effect-table {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .effect-item {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .effect-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #f97316;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .effect-value {
            color: #22d3ee;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .effect-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1), rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1));
            border: 2px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #eab308;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .highlight-title:before {
            content: "🔥";
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .system-declaration {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1), rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.1));
            border: 2px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .declaration-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #f97316;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        .declaration-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .nav-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
            color: #22d3ee;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
        }
        
        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .strategy-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .effect-table {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        /* 新添加的样式 - 计算公式卡片 */
        .formula-section {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        /* 新添加的样式 - 计算公式卡片 */
        .formula-section {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .formula-section h4 {
            color: #22d3ee;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .formula-box {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #22d3ee;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .formula-explanation {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .explanation-item {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #f97316;
        }
        
        .formula-detail {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .example-table table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .example-table th {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
            color: #22d3ee;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #22d3ee;
        }
        
        .example-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .example-table tr:hover {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.05);
        }
        
        /* 响应式表格优化 */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .example-table table {
                display: block;
                overflow-x: auto;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }
            
            .example-table th,
            .example-table td {
                min-width: 80px;
                padding: 8px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            
            .formula-box {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 12px;
            }
            
            .formula-explanation .explanation-item {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 8px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .example-table th,
            .example-table td {
                min-width: 70px;
                padding: 6px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
            
            .formula-box {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .card-title {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            
            .card-subtitle {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 页头 -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎯 Open-Gi-Oh! 平衡策略展示</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">系统暴君平衡策略思维链 v1.0</div>
            <div class="version">玩家血量: 30 | 创建时间: 2026-03-12 23:15</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 策略网格 -->
        <div class="strategy-grid">
            
            <!-- 固定规则卡片 -->
            <div class="strategy-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-title">固定规则 (不可协商)</div>
                        <div class="card-subtitle">所有Agent必须遵守的核心原则</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-content">
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-fixed">
                        <span class="rule-label label-fixed">固定规则</span>
                        <strong>相同战斗力必须对应相同费用</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：战斗力相同但费用不同</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">允许：不同愿望/性格/审美有不同战斗力计算公式</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">但费用转化关系必须一致</div>
                    
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-fixed" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <span class="rule-label label-fixed">固定规则</span>
                        <strong>交换能力合理范围</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">基础合理：同费用卡牌交换同费用卡牌</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">允许范围：最多交换比自己高1费用的卡牌</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：1费卡交换3费卡（过度赚取）</div>
                    
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-fixed" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <span class="rule-label label-fixed">固定规则</span>
                        <strong>特殊胜利条件</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">特殊胜利必须比常规胜利更难</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：特殊胜利比常规胜利更容易</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 可协商规则卡片 -->
            <div class="strategy-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">🤝</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-title">可协商规则</div>
                        <div class="card-subtitle">在边界内允许调整</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-content">
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-negotiable">
                        <span class="rule-label label-negotiable">可协商</span>
                        <strong>效果价值调整</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">允许：调整效果价值（±10%）</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">如：剧毒从5费调整为4.5-5.5费</div>
                    
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-negotiable" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <span class="rule-label label-negotiable">可协商</span>
                        <strong>计算公式系数</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">允许：微调战斗力计算公式系数（±20%）</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">如：攻击系数从1.0调整为0.8-1.2</div>
                    
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-negotiable" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <span class="rule-label label-negotiable">可协商</span>
                        <strong>新增效果类型</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">允许：增加新的效果类型</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">要求：需提供明确的价值评估</div>
                    
                    <div class="strategy-rule rule-prohibited" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <span class="rule-label label-prohibited">禁止</span>
                        <strong>禁止协商的边界</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：改变费用-战斗力核心关系</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：让低费卡过度赚取</div>
                    <div class="strategy-item">禁止：特殊胜利比常规胜利容易</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 费用-战斗力转换表卡片 -->
            <div class="strategy-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">💰</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-title">费用-战斗力转换表</div>
                        <div class="card-subtitle">基于30血量重新校准</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-content">
                    <table class="cost-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>费用</th>
                                <th>战斗力范围</th>
                                <th>类别</th>
                                <th>交换限制</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>0费</strong></td>
                                <td>0-5</td>
                                <td>工具牌</td>
                                <td>只能交换0-1费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>1费</strong></td>
                                <td>5-7</td>
                                <td>前期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换2费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>2费</strong></td>
                                <td>7-9</td>
                                <td>前期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换3费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>3费</strong></td>
                                <td>9-13</td>
                                <td>前期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换4费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>4费</strong></td>
                                <td>13-17</td>
                                <td>中期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换5费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>5费</strong></td>
                                <td>17-23</td>
                                <td>中期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换6费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>6费</strong></td>
                                <td>23-29</td>
                                <td>中期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换7费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>7费</strong></td>
                                <td>29-37</td>
                                <td>后期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换8费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>8费</strong></td>
                                <td>37-45</td>
                                <td>后期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换9费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>9费</strong></td>
                                <td>45-55</td>
                                <td>后期牌</td>
                                <td>最多交换10费卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>10费</strong></td>
                                <td>55-82</td>
                                <td>终结牌</td>
                                <td>应有终结游戏能力</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <div class="strategy-item" style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #94a3b8;">
                        * 基于30血量，游戏长度7-10回合，平均每回合费用3-5，10费战斗力是0费的12倍，范围无重叠确保唯一对应
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            </div>
            <!-- 愿望-性格-审美计算公式卡片 -->
            <div class="strategy-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">🧬</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-title">性格-战斗力计算公式（简化版）</div>
                        <div class="card-subtitle">仅性格影响战斗数值，5种公式覆盖所有组合</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-content">
                    <div class="formula-section">
                        <h4>核心理解修正：</h4>
                        <div class="formula-box">
                            ✅ 正确理解：偏向属性的系数应更低（反直觉设计）<br>
                            ❌ 错误理解：偏向属性的系数应更高（传统直觉）
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="formula-explanation">
                            <div class="explanation-item">
                                <strong>数学原理</strong><br>
                                <span class="formula-detail">战斗力 = 系数 × 数值</span><br>
                                <span class="formula-detail">系数低 → 同战斗力下数值更高（优势）</span><br>
                                <span class="formula-detail">系数高 → 同战斗力下数值更低（劣势）</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="explanation-item">
                                <strong>游戏意义</strong><br>
                                <span class="formula-detail">勇敢虾虾：攻击系数低(0.85) → 同费用下攻击力更高</span><br>
                                <span class="formula-detail">智慧虾虾：生命系数低(0.85) → 同费用下生命值更高</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">5种性格公式表：</h4>
                        <div class="example-table">
                            <table>
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>性格</th>
                                        <th>攻击系数</th>
                                        <th>生命系数</th>
                                        <th>基础系数</th>
                                        <th>描述</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>勇敢</strong></td>
                                        <td>0.85</td>
                                        <td>1.05</td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>攻击型虾虾，同费用下攻击力更高</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>智慧</strong></td>
                                        <td>1.05</td>
                                        <td>0.85</td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>防御型虾虾，同费用下生命值更高</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>狡猾</strong></td>
                                        <td>0.90</td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>敏捷型虾虾，攻击力略高</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>沉稳</strong></td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>0.90</td>
                                        <td>1.00</td>
                                        <td>稳重型虾虾，生命值略高</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>狂野</strong></td>
                                        <td>0.70</td>
                                        <td>0.70</td>
                                        <td>1.30</td>
                                        <td>极端型虾虾，高风险高回报</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="strategy-item" style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #94a3b8;">
                            * 简化设计：从125种组合优化为5种公式，仅性格影响计算<br>
                            * 核心原则：偏向属性的系数更低，确保同费用下的数值优势
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <!-- 特殊效果价值卡片 -->
            <div class="strategy-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">✨</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-title">特殊效果价值</div>
                        <div class="card-subtitle">战斗力价值评估</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-content">
